{"tid":589081,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"新 Lighting 設計具防水 插綫後滴水不侵","createTime":"2018-03-11T15:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T09:41:56.000Z","uid":13663,"like":10,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"5ea91401af57ac7ba30f87745fd3b0067d06f681","tid":589081,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T15:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2025000/2027329/20180310_Ricky_Lightning-1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2025000%2F2027329%2F20180310_Ricky_Lightning-1_1024.jpg&h=300e830e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nApple Lightning 插頭再掀變革，下世代將做成水密 (watertight) 設計，令液體不會滲在插頭與插座之間。但屆時肯定或改用全新的 Lightning 插頭與插座設計，舊版 Lightning 纜綫或未能繼續使用！<br />\n<br />\n自從 iPhone 7 及 Apple Watch 開始，Lightning 插座內部已加入了水密封環，但這樣還未夠。若 Lightning 插頭於充電期間，舉例因潮濕或氣溫突然變化，導致金屬接點表面有「水氣」 (凝結水)，依然會對裝置構成風險。所以 Apple 近期已向 USPTO (美國專利及商標局) 呈交了新的專利文件，揭示 Apple 已擬定了下世代 Lightning 插頭的新設計，令插頭本身也要做到水密！<br />\n<br />\n有了水密設計，當新 Lightning 插頭與插座已接合時，即使充電中途遇上潮濕或氣溫突然變化，也不怕損壞綫路、充電池或充電器等。新 Lightning 插座造成「楔形」形狀，而非現時的扁平狀。較特別是，若新 Lightning 插座一方是固定的裝置，譬如桌面式充電插座，廠商更可加設小型抽真空泵 (vacuum pump)，令插頭跟插座之間真空，更牢固地連接。繼而透過軟體方式，令插座還原至正常氣壓，繼而容許拔出插頭。<br />\n<br />\n話雖如此，註冊新專利純粹為保障知識產權，不代表一定會付諸實行。該專利文件中，未有提及舊版 Lightning 插頭的向後兼容性。<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=Mc4KseLfJtuR7deRXvtNef1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=6248b997\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a> 小編倒認為，若新 Lightning 插座不支援現時的扁平狀 Lightning 插頭，將有助杜絕泛濫於市面的「假綫」、「山寨綫」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Apple已死 請課金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c9716b0d7c7fb46f369564ce559ad5a8390b359","tid":589081,"uid":1557,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:33:45.000Z","msg":"又換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6d6c5d7dab7443e0fee574246159632b7907ae","tid":589081,"uid":1723,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T17:03:19.000Z","msg":"歐盟唔係要手機統一做usb-c 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係已經傾掂數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d543333781609533c597f21d5c1303bf198b277","tid":589081,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T17:12:57.000Z","msg":"好<br />\n出年照跟"},{"pid":"f2e804ebaf94e9869b3a9273961592fee1bb5c2d","tid":589081,"uid":1130,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T17:28:57.000Z","msg":"又換？ on99"},{"pid":"5695fae6beefd22092fbb3b6e4de953db1050103","tid":589081,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2e804ebaf94e9869b3a9273961592fee1bb5c2d","tid":589081,"uid":1130,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T17:28:57.000Z","msg":"又換？ on99"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T17:32:35.000Z","msg":"用左4年了"},{"pid":"192b7293f78c164fb2106e2c643d4e8d90a69a60","tid":589081,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T17:44:46.000Z","msg":"usbc 都係佢的，偏偏獨家整多套lighting <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b876898a66b14df53be9b632d2e1b918b77e9ffe","tid":589081,"uid":39710,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T06:42:32.000Z","msg":"全部變晒usb type c算啦屌"},{"pid":"7c490a69aa9fd691e7198a42452c18478019f010","tid":589081,"uid":81756,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c6d6c5d7dab7443e0fee574246159632b7907ae","tid":589081,"uid":1723,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T17:03:19.000Z","msg":"歐盟唔係要手機統一做usb-c 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係已經傾掂數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T06:43:22.000Z","msg":"唔賣歐盟都仲得啦<img src=\"/asse